# AWS Cloud Computing – Basics Activity
 
Today I learned the foundational concepts of **AWS Cloud Computing**.
 
### 🔹 What I Covered
• What is cloud computing  
• What is AWS (Amazon Web Services)  
• AWS global infrastructure  
• Regions and Availability Zones  
• Free Tier and pricing basics
 
### 📝 Key Points
• Cloud computing means renting compute, storage, networking on demand.  
• AWS provides services like EC2, S3, VPC, IAM, RDS.  
• Regions are geographic locations (e.g., Mumbai, Singapore, USA).  
• Availability Zones are separate datacenters in a region.  
• Free Tier gives limited free usage for 12 months to new accounts.
 
